Calendar
Download iCal File




Date: Monday, December 5th
Time: 2:00 – 5:00 PM CST
Location: SCE Room 213 (Montgomery Ward Gallery)

You don’t have to study alone! Study with other UIC Students and us at the Montgomery Ward Gallery. Free tea bags will be offered. Supplies are limited and I-card is required!


